high_descs: Move forward to the shelf in front of you.
Pick up the watermelon on the top shelf.
Turn around and walk to the sidetable between the sofa and chair.
Put the watermelon on the sidetable next to the other item.
Turn around, turn left, and move to the side of the sofa.
Pick up the watermelon from the couch.
Turn left and move to the sidetable on your right.
Put the slice of watermelon you're carrying in front of the slice of watermelon on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two slices of watermelon on the SideTable.

high_descs: Go to the shelf straight ahead.
Pick up the watermelon from the top shelf.
Turn around and go towards the sidetable.
Place the watermelon on the sidetable.
Turn towards the two-seat sofa to the right of the couch.
Pick up the watermelon.
Turn back towards the sidetable.
Place the watermelon on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two pieces of watermelon on a SideTable.

high_descs: Walk straight to the shelf in front of you.
Take a piece of watermelon from the top shelf.
Turn around and go all the way to the sidetable.
Place the watermelon on the sidetable.
Turn back and move to the right side of the sofa, then face the sofa.
Pick up a piece of watermelon from the sofa.
Go back to the sidetable.
Place the watermelon on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two pieces of watermelon, one from a shelf and another from the sofa, to place them on the round side table.
